val() should handle setting array of strings and select-multiple elements

commit.message:
Handle arrays when setting/getting with `val`

Allow setting/getting multiple values in array form for a
`select-multiple` element and stringify all other array inputs. Fixes
API inconsistency by only toggling select for the first `option` with a
matching value if multiple `option` elements have the same value.
